Based in Miami Florida, It’s undeniable that Chris has been crushing the house music scene with major releases on labels such as Juicy, Armada and Nervous Records. Over the course of his career, he has also been dominating mega venues and sharing the stage with artists such as, Axwell, Sebastian Ingrosso, Zedd, Diplo & many more to add to the long list.
